divs: Sighting Detailssimilar to triangle ufos on tv.this thing was big .over gas station,over road and over field.i just thought it was a new stealth bomber,years later i saw a stealth bomber and knew it was not that.now you see it on tv.it never moved.it made no sound.it was very unthreatening.i really didnt think it was a ufo.we finally just left and didnt talk to anyone.
